items.title: Develop a deeper understanding with interactive images in Gemini.
items.summary: A Gemini chat shares a diagram of a plant cell with various labels that are then shown in more detail in a side panel . Each label is highlighted and you can use the side panel to delve deeper into the diagram . The side panel is highlighted to highlight each label and show more detail of the cell in a new interactive version of the chat .

items.title: Google's upgraded Nano Banana Pro AI image model hailed as 'absolutely bonkers' for enterprises and users
items.summary: Google DeepMind’s Gemini 3 Pro Image is a model built to integrate deeply across Google's AI stack . It is capable of generating UX flows, educational diagrams, storyboards, and mockups from language prompts . The model supports output resolutions of up to 2K and 4K, and includes studio-level controls over camera angle, color grading, focus, and lighting .

items.title: ScaleOps' new AI Infra Product slashes GPU costs for self-hosted enterprise LLMs by 50% for early adopters
items.summary: ScaleOps has expanded its cloud resource management platform with a new product aimed at enterprises operating self-hosted large language models (LLMs) and GPU-based AI applications . The company said the system is already running in enterprise production environments and delivering major efficiency gains for early adopters, reducing GPU costs by between 50% and 70% . The product is designed for compatibility with common enterprise infrastructure patterns .

items.title: How we’re bringing AI image verification to the Gemini app
items.summary: Golden retriever catching frisbee over water . Google AI watermark detected detected . Google says watermark was detected by a machine in a lab lab . Google's watermark is now being used in the lab lab to detect watermarks . Google has been working with the lab to develop a lab that can detect water marks in labs in labs across the world .

items.title: Ai2’s Olmo 3 family challenges Qwen and Llama with efficient, open reasoning and customization
items.summary: Allen Institute for AI hopes to take advantage of an increased demand for customized models and enterprises seeking more transparency from AI models . Olmo 3 has a longer context window, more reasoning traces and is better at coding than its previous iteration . This latest version, like the other Olmo releases, is open-sourced under the Apache 2.0 license . Enterprises will have complete transparency into and control over the training data and checkpointing .
